          "_name": "features17",
          "_sourceTheme": "mobirise5",
          "_customHTML": "<section data-bs-version=\"5.1\" class=\"features17\" group=\"Features\" data-bg-video=\"{{bg.type == 'video' && bg.value.url}}\" mbr-class=\"{'mbr-parallax-background': bg.parallax}\">\n    <mbr-parameters>\n        <header>Size</header>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Full Width\" name=\"fullWidth\" checked>\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Top\" name=\"paddingTop\" min=\"0\" max=\"10\" step=\"1\" value=\"0\">\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Bottom\" name=\"paddingBottom\" min=\"0\" max=\"10\" step=\"1\" value=\"0\">\n        <input type=\"range\" name=\"imageWidth\" title=\"Image\" min=\"4\" max=\"8\" step=\"1\" value=\"5\">\n        <header>Show/Hide</header>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Title\" name=\"showTitle\">\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Text\" name=\"showText\" checked>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Buttons\" name=\"showButtons\" checked>\n        <input type=\"color\" title=\"Card Color\" name=\"cardColor\" value=\"#ffffff\" selected>\n        <header>Background</header>\n        <fieldset type=\"background\" name=\"bg\" parallax>\n            <input type=\"image\" title=\"Image\" value=\"../_images/background3.jpg\">\n            <input type=\"color\" title=\"Color\" value=\"#ffffff\" selected>\n            <input type=\"video\" title=\"Video\" value=\"https://vimeo.com/428046504\">\n        </fieldset>\n        <header condition=\"bg.type === 'video'\">Fallback Image</header>\n        <input type=\"image\" title=\"Fallback Image\" value=\"../_images/background13.jpg\" name=\"fallBackImage\" condition=\"bg.type === 'video'\">\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Overlay\" name=\"overlay\" condition=\"bg.type !== 'color'\" checked>\n        <input type=\"color\" title=\"Overlay Color\" name=\"overlayColor\" value=\"#ffffff\" condition=\"overlay && bg.type !== 'color'\">\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Opacity\" name=\"overlayOpacity\" min=\"0\" max=\"1\" step=\"0.1\" value=\"0.5\" condition=\"overlay && bg.type !== 'color'\">\n    </mbr-parameters>\n\n    <div class=\"mbr-fallback-image disabled\" mbr-if=\"bg.type == 'video'\"></div>\n    <div class=\"mbr-overlay\" mbr-if=\"overlay && bg.type!== 'color'\" mbr-style=\"{'opacity': overlayOpacity, 'background-color': overlayColor}\">\n    </div>\n    <div mbr-class=\"{'container': !fullWidth, 'container-fluid': fullWidth}\">\n        <div class=\"content-wrapper\">\n            <div class=\"row align-items-center\">\n                <div class=\"col-12 col-lg-{{imageWidth}}\">\n                    <div class=\"image-wrapper\">\n                        <img src=\"@PROJECT_PATH@/assets/images/joesephswell-1.webp\" alt=\"Joseph's Well\">\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"col-12 col-lg\">\n                    <div class=\"text-wrapper\">\n                        <h6 class=\"card-title mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-5\" mbr-if=\"showTitle\" data-app-selector=\".card-title\">\n                            <b>Easy and simple</b>\n                        </h6>\n                        <p class=\"mbr-text mbr-fonts-style mb-4\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" mbr-if=\"showText\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-text, .mbr-section-btn\"><b>Joseph’s Well System</b> is a comprehensive and step-by-step guide that will teach you how to produce clean and safe water for drinking by utilizing the air around you. The system works by utilizing a brilliant technique called “Atmospheric Water Generation,” which simply means it extracts water from the air and uses it to produce clean and purified water that you can use daily. This concept may sound quite unexpected at first, but it’s really a natural solution to problems like water scarcity and lack of water supply.<br>\n<br>What makes this system really special is how simple and easy it is to follow. You don’t need to be an expert or have any technical skills. Everything is explained in a very clear and friendly way. The program includes easy-to-follow video tutorials, detailed building plans, and a list of low-cost materials that you can find in most local stores. With just basic tools and a little time, you can build the system yourself at home.<br>\n<br>The amount of water you can produce depends on how much moisture is in the air where you live, but in many cases, it can generate several gallons of water every day. This makes it very useful for people who live off the grid, want to be prepared for emergencies, or simply wish to depend less on city water systems.&nbsp;<br></p>\n                        <div mbr-buttons mbr-theme-style=\"display-4\" class=\"mbr-section-btn mt-3\" mbr-if=\"showButtons\"><a class=\"btn btn-primary\" data-app-placeholder=\"Type Text\" href=\"https://e31dceh5oryjfp1t7qdhljdr3a.hop.clickbank.net/?&traffic_source=org\"><span class=\"mobi-mbri mobi-mbri-cursor-click mbr-iconfont mbr-iconfont-btn\"></span>Visit official Website</a> <a class=\"btn btn-primary\" data-app-placeholder=\"Type Text\" href=\"https://e31dceh5oryjfp1t7qdhljdr3a.hop.clickbank.net/?&traffic_source=org\"><span class=\"mobi-mbri mobi-mbri-cursor-click mbr-iconfont mbr-iconfont-btn\"></span>Click Here To Buy Now</a></div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n</section>",
