        {
          "_name": "content5",
          "_sourceTheme": "mobirise5",
          "_customHTML": "<section data-bs-version=\"5.1\" class=\"content5\" group=\"Content\">\n    <mbr-parameters>\n        <header>Size</header>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Full Width\" name=\"fullWidth\">\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Top\" name=\"paddingTop\" min=\"0\" max=\"10\" step=\"1\" value=\"3\">\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Bottom\" name=\"paddingBottom\" min=\"0\" max=\"10\" step=\"1\" value=\"2\">\n        <input type=\"range\" name=\"textWidth\" title=\"Width\" min=\"4\" max=\"12\" value=\"12\" step=\"1\">\n        <header>Show/Hide</header>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Title\" name=\"showTitle\">\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Subtitle\" name=\"showSubtitle\">\n        <header>Background</header>\n        <input type=\"color\" title=\"Color\" name=\"bgColor\" value=\"#ffffff\">\n    </mbr-parameters>\n    <div mbr-class=\"{'container': !fullWidth, 'container-fluid': fullWidth}\">\n        <div class=\"row justify-content-center\">\n            <div class=\"col-md-12 col-lg-{{textWidth}}\">\n                <h3 class=\"mbr-section-title mbr-fonts-style mb-4\" mbr-if=\"showTitle\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-section-title\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-2\">\n                    <b>Article Title</b>\n                </h3>\n                <h4 class=\"mbr-section-subtitle mbr-fonts-style mb-4\" mbr-if=\"showSubtitle\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-section-subtitle\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-5\">\n                    Enter your subtitle here\n                </h4>\n                <p class=\"mbr-text mbr-fonts-style\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-text\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-4\">The Joseph’s Well System is built on the proven science of Atmospheric Water Generation (AWG)—a method that captures moisture from the air and turns it into clean, drinkable water. It works by pulling in humid air, cooling it until water vapor condenses, and then collecting and purifying that water into safe, refreshing drinking water. This technology allows you to create fresh water straight from the atmosphere—a resource that’s becoming increasingly important in today’s unpredictable climate.<br>\n<br>The most distinctive feature of Joseph’s Well is its simplicity and ease of use. You don’t need technical expertise, engineering skills, or expensive equipment. You can use affordable materials from most hardware stores, and anyone can build the system without any technical knowledge, engineering skills, or expensive equipment, as it is easy to do and use, and it can be run manually, with little electricity, or even by solar power.<br>\n<br>The program provides detailed video tutorials, construction blueprints, and a full materials list, guiding you through every step from start to finish. Whether you’re a DIY novice or an experienced builder, the instructions are straightforward and easy to follow. With the right setup, Joseph’s Well can produce several gallons of pure, clean water each day, depending on your local humidity and environmental conditions.&nbsp;<br></p>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n</section>",
