          "_name": "article17",
          "_sourceTheme": "startm5",
          "_customHTML": "<section data-bs-version=\"5.1\" class=\"article17\" group=\"Article\">\n  <mbr-parameters>\n    <header>Size</header>\n    <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Full Width\" name=\"fullWidth\">\n    <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Top\" name=\"paddingTop\" min=\"0\" max=\"10\" step=\"1\" value=\"2\">\n    <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Bottom\" name=\"paddingBottom\" min=\"0\" max=\"10\" step=\"1\" value=\"1\">\n    <input type=\"range\" name=\"textWidth\" title=\"Width\" min=\"4\" max=\"12\" value=\"11\" step=\"1\">\n    <header>Show/Hide</header>\n    <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Title\" name=\"showMainTitle\">\n    <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Subtitle\" name=\"showMainSubtitle\" checked>\n    <input type=\"color\" name=\"iconColor\" title=\"Color\" value=\"#3a341c\">\n    <header>Background</header>\n    <input type=\"color\" title=\"Color\" name=\"bgColor\" value=\"#ffffff\">\n  </mbr-parameters>\n\n  <div mbr-class=\"{'container': !fullWidth, 'container-fluid': fullWidth}\">\n    <div class=\"row justify-content-center\">\n      <div class=\"counter-container col-md-12 col-lg-{{textWidth}}\">\n        <div class=\"row mb-5 justify-content-center\" mbr-if=\"showMainTitle || showMainSubtitle\">\n          <div class=\"col-12 content-head\">\n            <h3 class=\"mbr-section-title mbr-fonts-style align-center mb-0\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-2\" mbr-if=\"showMainTitle\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-section-title\">\n              <b>List</b>\n            </h3>\n            <h5 class=\"mbr-section-subtitle mbr-fonts-style align-center mb-0 mt-4\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" mbr-if=\"showMainSubtitle\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-section-subtitle\">With Joseph’s Well, creating your own reliable water supply has never been easier. By combining instant digital access, affordable materials, and beginner-friendly instructions, the system empowers anyone to build a fully functional water generator—no prior experience required. Whether you’re preparing for emergencies, living off the grid, or simply seeking more self-sufficiency, Joseph’s Well gives you the tools to take control of your water needs with confidence.\n<div><br></div></h5>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"mbr-text mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-text\" data-multiline mbr-article>\n          <ol>\n            <li><b>Instant Digital Access:</b>&nbsp;Right after your purchase, you get immediate access to the complete Joseph’s Well System. Download the full package directly to your device and start learning with step-by-step video tutorials, printable blueprints, and comprehensive building instructions. You can begin planning and constructing your system right away—no waiting, no shipping delays.</li><li><b>Easy-to-Find Materials:</b>&nbsp;The program includes a detailed materials list with affordable, easy-to-source parts available at most local hardware stores or online. There’s no need for rare components, expensive tools, or specialized equipment—everything you need is accessible, budget-friendly, and ready for you to start building.</li>\n            <li><b>Beginner-Friendly Instructions: </b>The design of Joseph’s Well is simple. With clear and guided instructions, diagrams, and easy-to-follow explanations, the system will guide you through every step of the way. Whether you are a complete novice or a seasoned DIY enthusiast, the instructions are easy to follow and make building your own water generator a smooth and efficient process for you.</li>\n          </ol>\n          <ol>\n          </ol>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</section>",
