          "_name": "article17",
          "_sourceTheme": "startm5",
          "_customHTML": "<section data-bs-version=\"5.1\" class=\"article17\" group=\"Article\">\n  <mbr-parameters>\n    <header>Size</header>\n    <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Full Width\" name=\"fullWidth\">\n    <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Top\" name=\"paddingTop\" min=\"0\" max=\"10\" step=\"1\" value=\"1\">\n    <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Bottom\" name=\"paddingBottom\" min=\"0\" max=\"10\" step=\"1\" value=\"1\">\n    <input type=\"range\" name=\"textWidth\" title=\"Width\" min=\"4\" max=\"12\" value=\"11\" step=\"1\">\n    <header>Show/Hide</header>\n    <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Title\" name=\"showMainTitle\">\n    <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Subtitle\" name=\"showMainSubtitle\" checked>\n    <input type=\"color\" name=\"iconColor\" title=\"Color\" value=\"#3a341c\">\n    <header>Background</header>\n    <input type=\"color\" title=\"Color\" name=\"bgColor\" value=\"#ffffff\">\n  </mbr-parameters>\n\n  <div mbr-class=\"{'container': !fullWidth, 'container-fluid': fullWidth}\">\n    <div class=\"row justify-content-center\">\n      <div class=\"counter-container col-md-12 col-lg-{{textWidth}}\">\n        <div class=\"row mb-5 justify-content-center\" mbr-if=\"showMainTitle || showMainSubtitle\">\n          <div class=\"col-12 content-head\">\n            <h3 class=\"mbr-section-title mbr-fonts-style align-center mb-0\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-2\" mbr-if=\"showMainTitle\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-section-title\">\n              <b>List</b>\n            </h3>\n            <h5 class=\"mbr-section-subtitle mbr-fonts-style align-center mb-0 mt-4\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" mbr-if=\"showMainSubtitle\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-section-subtitle\"><div>The Joseph’s Well System combines reliability, simplicity, and sustainability to provide clean, drinkable water straight from the air. Designed with beginners in mind and built using affordable, easy-to-find materials, it requires no plumbing, no technical skills, and no expensive equipment. Whether you’re living off-grid, preparing for emergencies, or looking for a dependable everyday water source, Joseph’s Well offers a practical, eco-friendly solution that can be powered by solar energy. With built-in purification and optional mineralization, it ensures your family has access to safe, healthy, and great-tasting water anytime, anywhere. Inspired by faith and focused on self-reliance, Joseph’s Well empowers you to take full control of your water needs with confidence and peace of mind.</div></h5>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"mbr-text mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-text\" data-multiline mbr-article>\n          <ol>\n            <li><b>Reliable Water Source — Anytime, Anywhere:</b>&nbsp;Joseph’s Well System provides a dependable way to create clean, drinkable water directly from the air—no rivers, rainfall, or plumbing required. Using advanced Atmospheric Water Generation (AWG) technology, it captures humidity from the surrounding environment and converts it into fresh, safe water. This makes it ideal for remote locations, off-grid living, drought-prone areas, or emergency preparedness. Unlike rain barrels, which rely on unpredictable weather, or wells, which require digging and maintenance, Joseph’s Well operates daily in most climates. Families can feel secure knowing they have a steady, independent water supply available anytime, anywhere.</li><li><b>No Plumbing or Technical Skills Required:</b>&nbsp;Joseph’s Well is meant for all people, from first-time DIY enthusiasts to seasoned hobbyists. No knowledge of plumbing, engineering, or technical skills are required. It comes with video tutorials that are easy to follow, diagrams, and a list of materials that are complete. It is easy and stress-free to do everything. It has also been a fun weekend project for many families. Teens and adults alike can get involved. There is no need to spend money hiring expensive contractors or purchasing expensive tools. Just basic tools found at home are all that are required.</li>\n            <li><b>Low-Cost and Easy to Build:</b><b style=\"font-size: calc(1.28rem + 0.52 * ((100vw - 62rem) / 25));\">&nbsp;</b><span style=\"font-size: calc(1.28rem + 0.52 * ((100vw - 62rem) / 25));\">Affordability is a core feature of Joseph’s Well. Most users can build the entire system for under $150, using inexpensive, widely available materials from local hardware stores or online. There are no ongoing fees, complicated components, or high-cost filters to worry about. Once assembled, the system requires minimal maintenance and operates efficiently day after day. Compared to deep wells, commercial water generators, or bottled water solutions, Joseph’s Well offers a cost-effective, long-term solution for families seeking preparedness, security, and peace of mind without breaking the budget.\n</span></li><li><b style=\"font-size: calc(1.28rem + 0.52 * ((100vw - 62rem) / 25));\">Solar and Off-Grid Capable: </b><span style=\"font-size: calc(1.28rem + 0.52 * ((100vw - 62rem) / 25));\">One of Joseph’s Well’s greatest strengths is its off-grid capability. It can run on standard household electricity or be powered entirely by solar energy, making it perfect for cabins, RVs, rural properties, and other off-grid locations. Even during power outages, Joseph’s Well continues to produce water, ensuring you and your family remain supplied with clean drinking water when you need it most. Its energy flexibility makes it ideal for anyone seeking independence from public utilities and eco-conscious households wanting to reduce their environmental impact.</span></li><li><span style=\"font-size: calc(1.28rem + 0.52 * ((100vw - 62rem) / 25));\"><b>Clean, Filtered, and Mineralized Water: </b>Joseph’s Well does more than just generate water—it delivers pure, healthy, great-tasting water. The system includes guidance for multi-stage filtration and mineralization, removing impurities while restoring essential minerals for optimal taste and health. Unlike stored or stagnant water, Joseph’s Well produces fresh water on demand, free from harmful chemicals or contaminants. This is especially valuable in areas where tap water may be unreliable, heavily treated, or unpalatable. With Joseph’s Well, every drop your family drinks is clean, nourishing, and safe.</span></li><li><span style=\"font-size: calc(1.28rem + 0.52 * ((100vw - 62rem) / 25));\"><b>Ideal for Emergencies and Disasters</b>: Water is often the first resource to disappear during disasters. Joseph’s Well provides a dependable backup supply during hurricanes, blackouts, droughts, or infrastructure failures. Because it operates independently from public utilities, it continues producing clean water even when traditional systems fail. Compact, quiet, and solar-compatible, it’s perfect for emergency kits, preparedness plans, or off-grid living. There’s no need to hoard bottled water or bulky containers—Joseph’s Well gives you peace of mind knowing your family will always have safe drinking water, no matter what happens.\n</span></li><li><span style=\"font-size: calc(1.28rem + 0.52 * ((100vw - 62rem) / 25));\"><b>Environmentally Friendly Water Solution: </b>Joseph’s Well is a sustainable, eco-conscious alternative to bottled water or municipal systems. By generating water directly from the air, it reduces plastic waste, transportation needs, and resource-intensive extraction. Its solar compatibility further lowers energy consumption and carbon footprint, making it ideal for environmentally conscious households. With Joseph’s Well, you’re not just providing water for your family—you’re protecting natural resources and the planet, all while enjoying a consistent, high-quality water supply.\n</span></li><li><span style=\"font-size: calc(1.28rem + 0.52 * ((100vw - 62rem) / 25));\"><b>Empowering Faith-Based and Self-Reliant Living: </b>However, <a href=\"https://joesephwell.com\" class=\"text-black\">Joseph’s Well</a> is more than just a water system; it is a mission statement built on the principles of faith, stewardship, and self-sufficiency. With biblical principles of preparedness and provision as the guiding force, Joseph’s Well is designed to promote self-sufficiency for the family while caring for the ones you love. Whether you are a person of faith or not, Joseph’s Well is the right answer for you. With its principles of preparedness and provision, you know you have the security and peace of mind you need. Whether you are looking for emergency preparedness or the self-sufficiency lifestyle, Joseph’s Well is the answer for you.</span></li>\n          </ol>\n          <ol>\n          </ol>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</section>",
