          "_name": "features032",
          "_sourceTheme": "startm5",
          "_customHTML": "<section data-bs-version=\"5.1\" class=\"features032\" group=\"Features\" data-bg-video=\"{{bg.type == 'video' && bg.value.url}}\" mbr-class=\"{'mbr-parallax-background': bg.parallax}\">\n  <mbr-parameters>\n    <header>Size</header>\n    <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Full Width\" name=\"fullWidth\">\n    <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Top\" name=\"paddingTop\" min=\"0\" max=\"10\" step=\"1\" value=\"3\">\n    <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Bottom\" name=\"paddingBottom\" min=\"0\" max=\"10\" step=\"1\" value=\"1\">\n    <header>Show/Hide</header>\n    <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Title\" name=\"showMainTitle\">\n    <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Subtitle\" name=\"showMainSubtitle\">\n    <header>Card</header>\n    <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Title\" name=\"showTitle\" checked>\n    <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Text\" name=\"showText\" checked>\n    <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Images\" name=\"showImages\">\n    <select title=\"Columns\" name=\"columns\">\n      <option value=\"12\">1</option>\n      <option value=\"6\" selected>2</option>\n      <option value=\"4\">3</option>\n      <option value=\"3\">4</option>\n    </select>\n    <input type=\"color\" title=\"Cards BG\" name=\"cardbg\" value=\"#edefeb\" selected>\n    <header>Background</header>\n    <fieldset type=\"background\" name=\"bg\" parallax>\n      <input type=\"image\" title=\"Image\" value=\"../_images/background1.jpg\">\n      <input type=\"color\" title=\"Color\" value=\"#ffffff\" selected>\n      <input type=\"video\" title=\"Video\" value=\"https://vimeo.com/428046504\">\n    </fieldset>\n    <header condition=\"bg.type === 'video'\">Fallback Image</header>\n    <input type=\"image\" title=\"Fallback Image\" value=\"../_images/background1.jpg\" name=\"fallBackImage\" condition=\"bg.type === 'video'\">\n    <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Overlay\" name=\"overlay\" condition=\"bg.type !== 'color'\">\n    <input type=\"color\" title=\"Overlay Color\" name=\"overlayColor\" value=\"#ffffff\" condition=\"overlay && bg.type !== 'color'\">\n    <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Opacity\" name=\"overlayOpacity\" min=\"0\" max=\"1\" step=\"0.1\" value=\"0.5\" condition=\"overlay && bg.type !== 'color'\">\n  </mbr-parameters>\n\n  <div class=\"mbr-fallback-image disabled\" mbr-if=\"bg.type == 'video'\"></div>\n  <div class=\"mbr-overlay\" mbr-if=\"overlay && bg.type!== 'color'\" mbr-style=\"{'opacity': overlayOpacity, 'background-color': overlayColor}\"></div>\n  <div mbr-class=\"{'container': !fullWidth, 'container-fluid': fullWidth}\">\n    <div class=\"row justify-content-center\">\n      <div class=\"col-12 mb-5 content-head\" mbr-if=\"showMainTitle || showMainSubtitle\">\n        <h3 class=\"mbr-section-title mbr-fonts-style align-center mb-0\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-2\" mbr-if=\"showMainTitle\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-section-title\">\n          <b>Our Features</b>\n        </h3>\n        <h5 class=\"mbr-section-subtitle mbr-fonts-style align-center mb-0 mt-4\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" mbr-if=\"showMainSubtitle\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-section-subtitle\">Emergency-Ready Water Supply\n<div>&nbsp;Joseph’s Well provides a reliable backup source of clean water during natural disasters, power outages, or droughts. It ensures your family stays hydrated even when public water systems fail.</div></h5>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"row\">\n      \n      <div class=\"item features-without-image col-12 col-lg-{{columns}} item-mb active\">\n        <div class=\"item-wrapper\">\n          <div class=\"card-box align-left\">\n            <div class=\"img-wrapper mb-3\" mbr-if=\"showImages\">\n              <img class src=\"../_images/shop/shop3.jpg\" data-slide-to=\"1\" data-bs-slide-to=\"1\">\n            </div>\n            <h5 class=\"card-title mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-5\" mbr-if=\"showTitle\" data-app-selector=\".card-title, .iconfont-wrapper\">\n              <b>Pros</b>\n            </h5>\n            <p class=\"card-text mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-4\" mbr-if=\"showText\" data-app-selector=\".card-text\">▪️ <b>Emergency-Ready Water Supply</b><br>Joseph’s Well provides a reliable backup source of clean water during natural disasters, power outages, or droughts. It ensures your family stays hydrated even when public water systems fail.<br><br>▪️&nbsp;<b>Safe, Clean, and Mineralized Water</b><br> The system produces fresh, purified water, and includes an optional mineralization feature to enhance taste and health benefits—perfect for everyday drinking and cooking.\n<br><br>▪️&nbsp;<b>Off-Grid and Solar Compatible</b><br> Whether powered by standard electricity or solar energy, Joseph’s Well works anywhere. It’s ideal for remote locations, RVs, cabins, or households seeking energy independence.<br><br>▪️&nbsp;<b>Budget-Friendly Solution\n</b><br> Designed to be affordable, most users can build the complete system for under $150 using easy-to-find materials from local stores or online.<br><br>▪️&nbsp;<b>Simple to Build and Operate\n</b><br> With beginner-friendly instructions, step-by-step video tutorials, and clear blueprints, anyone can assemble Joseph’s Well. No technical skills or specialized tools are required, making it a smooth and stress-free DIY project for the whole family.<br></p>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"item features-without-image col-12 col-lg-{{columns}} item-mb\">\n        <div class=\"item-wrapper\">\n          <div class=\"card-box align-left\">\n            <div class=\"img-wrapper mb-3\" mbr-if=\"showImages\">\n              <img class src=\"../_images/shop/shop2.jpg\" data-slide-to=\"2\" data-bs-slide-to=\"2\">\n            </div>\n            <h5 class=\"card-title mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-5\" mbr-if=\"showTitle\" data-app-selector=\".card-title, .iconfont-wrapper\">\n              <b>Cons</b></h5>\n            <p class=\"card-text mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-4\" mbr-if=\"showText\" data-app-selector=\".card-text\">\n              ▪️ <b>Output Depends on Humidity\n</b><br>Water production varies with humidity levels. In extremely dry climates, the daily water output may be lower than in more humid regions.<br><br></p>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n      \n      \n      \n    </div>\n  </div>\n</section>",
