        {
          "alias": false,
          "_styles": {
            "padding-top": "(@paddingTop * 1rem)",
            "padding-bottom": "(@paddingBottom * 1rem)",
            "background-color": "@bgColor"
          },
          "_name": "content5",
          "_sourceTheme": "mobirise5",
          "_customHTML": "<section data-bs-version=\"5.1\" class=\"content5\" group=\"Content\">\n    <mbr-parameters>\n        <header>Size</header>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Full Width\" name=\"fullWidth\" checked>\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Top\" name=\"paddingTop\" min=\"0\" max=\"10\" step=\"1\" value=\"5\">\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Bottom\" name=\"paddingBottom\" min=\"0\" max=\"10\" step=\"1\" value=\"5\">\n        <input type=\"range\" name=\"textWidth\" title=\"Width\" min=\"4\" max=\"12\" value=\"10\" step=\"1\">\n        <header>Show/Hide</header>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Title\" name=\"showTitle\" checked>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Subtitle\" name=\"showSubtitle\" checked>\n        <header>Background</header>\n        <input type=\"color\" title=\"Color\" name=\"bgColor\" value=\"#ffffff\">\n    </mbr-parameters>\n    <div mbr-class=\"{'container': !fullWidth, 'container-fluid': fullWidth}\">\n        <div class=\"row justify-content-center\">\n            <div class=\"col-md-12 col-lg-{{textWidth}}\">\n                <h3 class=\"mbr-section-title mbr-fonts-style mb-4\" mbr-if=\"showTitle\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-section-title\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-2\">\n                    <b>Privacy Policy</b></h3>\n                <h4 class=\"mbr-section-subtitle mbr-fonts-style mb-4\" mbr-if=\"showSubtitle\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-section-subtitle\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-5\">Privacy Policy for Joseph's Well</h4>\n                <p class=\"mbr-text mbr-fonts-style\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-text\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\">At Joseph's Well, accessible from ElectroSlim.com, we prioritize your privacy and are committed to protecting any information collected through your use of our website and products. This Privacy Policy explains what information is collected by Josephs Well, how it is used, and your rights concerning your personal information.<br><br>If you have questions or need further clarification regarding our Privacy Policy, please feel free to contact us.<br><br>Consent<br>By using our website, you agree to the terms of our Privacy Policy and consent to the collection and use of information as outlined.<br><br>Information We Collect<br>Information You Provide to Us<br>When you interact with Josephs Well, we may collect the following personal information based on your actions on the site:<br><br>Contact Information: Your name, email address, and phone number.<br>Payment and Billing Information: When you make a purchase, we collect your billing address, payment details, and other relevant billing information.<br>Other Voluntary Information: Any other information you choose to provide, such as feedback or inquiries through our support channels.<br>Automatically Collected Information<br>Our website uses tracking technologies such as cookies and web beacons to automatically collect data about your visit:<br><br>Device Information: Your device type, IP address, operating system, and browser type.<br>Usage Information: Information on how you navigate and use our site, including pages visited, links clicked, and date and time of access.<br>How We Use Your Information<br>We use the information we collect in several ways to enhance and personalize your experience with Josephs Well, including:<br><br>Processing Orders: To process and fulfill your purchases.<br>Customer Support: To address any inquiries, requests, or support needs.<br>Site Improvement: To optimize and improve our website’s functionality and user experience.<br>Marketing and Promotions: To provide updates on our products, exclusive offers, and other marketing communications (with your consent).<br>Data Security and Fraud Prevention: To maintain the security of our site and protect against unauthorized access or other harmful activity.<br>Data Sharing and Disclosure<br>Josephs Well does not sell, rent, or share your personal information with third parties, except in the following instances:<br><br>Service Providers: We may share your information with trusted third-party vendors who assist in operating our website, conducting business, or servicing your orders, as long as these parties agree to keep your information confidential.<br>Legal Requirements: We may release information if legally obligated to do so to comply with the law, enforce our policies, or protect the rights, safety, and property of Josephs well and its users.<br>Cookies and Tracking Technologies<br>Josephs well uses cookies and similar technologies to collect data to improve user experience and analyze website traffic. You can manage cookie preferences through your browser settings, but disabling cookies may limit certain functionalities of our site.<br><br>Your Privacy Rights<br>Josephs well respects your data privacy rights, and you may exercise the following rights as applicable:<br><br>Access: Request a copy of your personal information held by us.<br>Correction: Request corrections to inaccurate or incomplete information.<br>Deletion: Request deletion of your personal data, under certain conditions.<br>Objection: Object to certain processing activities, such as marketing communications.<br>Data Portability: Request that we transfer your data to another organization or directly to you.<br>If you wish to exercise any of these rights, please contact us, and we will respond within one month.<br><br>Data Security<br>We implement appropriate security measures to safeguard your personal information against unauthorized access, alteration, disclosure, or destruction. However, no method of transmission over the internet or electronic storage is completely secure, so we cannot guarantee absolute security.<br><br>Children’s Privacy<br>Josephs well is not intended for use by children under the age of 13, and we do not knowingly collect personal data from children. If we become aware that we have inadvertently collected such data, we will take prompt action to delete it.<br><br>Changes to This Privacy Policy<br>We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. Any changes will be posted on this page, and, where appropriate, we will notify you via email. We encourage you to review this page periodically.<br><br>Contact Us<br>For any questions, concerns, or requests regarding this Privacy Policy, please contact us at:<br><br>Email: Support@Joseph'sWell.com<br></p>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n</section>",
