          "_name": "content5",
          "_sourceTheme": "mobirise5",
          "_customHTML": "<section data-bs-version=\"5.1\" class=\"content5\" group=\"Content\">\n    <mbr-parameters>\n        <header>Size</header>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Full Width\" name=\"fullWidth\">\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Top\" name=\"paddingTop\" min=\"0\" max=\"10\" step=\"1\" value=\"5\">\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Bottom\" name=\"paddingBottom\" min=\"0\" max=\"10\" step=\"1\" value=\"5\">\n        <input type=\"range\" name=\"textWidth\" title=\"Width\" min=\"4\" max=\"12\" value=\"10\" step=\"1\">\n        <header>Show/Hide</header>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Title\" name=\"showTitle\" checked>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Subtitle\" name=\"showSubtitle\" checked>\n        <header>Background</header>\n        <input type=\"color\" title=\"Color\" name=\"bgColor\" value=\"#ffffff\">\n    </mbr-parameters>\n    <div mbr-class=\"{'container': !fullWidth, 'container-fluid': fullWidth}\">\n        <div class=\"row justify-content-center\">\n            <div class=\"col-md-12 col-lg-{{textWidth}}\">\n                <h3 class=\"mbr-section-title mbr-fonts-style mb-4\" mbr-if=\"showTitle\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-section-title\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-2\"><b>Terms and Conditions</b></h3>\n                <h4 class=\"mbr-section-subtitle mbr-fonts-style mb-4\" mbr-if=\"showSubtitle\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-section-subtitle\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-5\">Terms and Conditions for Josephs Well</h4>\n                <p class=\"mbr-text mbr-fonts-style\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-text\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\">Welcome to Josephs Well!<br><br>These terms and conditions outline the rules and regulations for using the Josephs Well website, located at - joesephwell.com - By accessing this website, we assume you accept these terms and conditions. Do not continue to use Josephs Well if you do not agree to all the terms and conditions stated on this page.<br><br>Terminology In these Terms and Conditions, “Client,” “You,” and “Your” refers to you, the person using this website and compliant with the Company’s terms and conditions. “The Company,” “Ourselves,” “We,” “Our,” and “Us” refers to our Company. Any use of the above terminology or other words in the singular, plural, capitalization, and/or he/she or they, are taken as interchangeable and refer to the same.<br><br>Cookies We use cookies on our website to improve your experience. By accessing Josephs Well, you agree to use cookies as per our Privacy Policy. Cookies help us retrieve your information each time you visit and enable certain functionalities on our website.<br><br>License Unless otherwise stated, Josephs Well and/or its licensors own the intellectual property rights for all material on Josephs Well. All intellectual property rights are reserved. You may access this from Josephs Well for your personal use, subject to restrictions set in these terms and conditions.<br><br>You must not:<br><br>Republish material from JosephsWell<br>Sell, rent, or sub-license material from JosephsWell<br>Reproduce, duplicate, or copy material from JosephsWell<br>Redistribute content from JosephsWell without permission<br>User Comments and Content Our website may allow users to post and exchange opinions and information. JosephsWell does not filter, edit, or review Comments before their presence on the website. Comments do not reflect the views of JosephsWell or its agents/affiliates. JosephsWell will not be liable for the Comments or any liability resulting from them.<br><br>We reserve the right to monitor Comments and remove those that are deemed inappropriate, offensive, or violate these Terms and Conditions. By posting comments, you agree:<br><br>You own the necessary rights to post the Comments.<br>Comments do not infringe on any third-party intellectual property rights.<br>Comments do not contain defamatory, libelous, offensive, or unlawful content.<br>Hyperlinking to Our Content Certain organizations may link to our Website without prior written approval:<br><br>Government agencies<br>Search engines<br>News organizations<br>Accredited businesses<br>We may consider other link requests from various organizations. Approved entities may hyperlink to our website, provided it is not deceptive and does not falsely imply sponsorship or endorsement.<br><br>Content Liability We are not responsible for any content appearing on third-party sites that link to our Website. You agree to protect and defend us against all claims arising from your Website. No link(s) should appear on any website that may be considered libelous, obscene, or criminal, or that violates any third-party rights.<br><br>Reservation of Rights We reserve the right to request that you remove any or all links to our website. By continuing to link to our Website, you agree to be bound by these linking terms and conditions.<br><br>Removal of Links from Our Website If you find any link on our website offensive, please inform us. We will consider requests to remove links, but we are not obligated to do so or to respond directly.<br><br>Limitation of Liability To the fullest extent permitted by law, JosephsWell excludes all warranties and conditions related to our website and the use of this website. Nothing in this disclaimer will:<br><br>Limit or exclude our or your liability for death or personal injury.<br>Limit or exclude our or your liability for fraud.<br>Exclude any liabilities that cannot be excluded by law.<br>The limitations and prohibitions of liability in this Section govern all liabilities arising under the disclaimer, including those in contract, tort, and for breach of statutory duty.<br><br>Disclaimer The information provided on this website is for general information purposes only. JosephsWell is not liable for any loss or damage incurred from using the website or its content.<br><br>Changes to These Terms We may revise these terms at any time. By continuing to use the website, you agree to abide by the current Terms and Conditions.<br><br>If you have any questions regarding these Terms and Conditions, please contact us at efty@gmail.com.</p>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n</section>",
          "_cid": "tLGdvaL88b",
